name: Air Strike Pro 2019: Sky War
description:
Air Strike 2019 brings you the most realistic and thrilling fighter jet game of the year. Climb into the cockpit and take control of the most advanced fighter jets and lead your nation to victory.

Defend your airbases, Sink enemy Naval Fleets and conquer skies. Earn new ranks as you complete more and more thrilling missions. Start your journey as a flight officer and pave your way to become a squadron leader.

The game consist of thrill packed action strategies, shoot missiles of different forms to take down your enemy, become the best pilot.
